					How To Install PHP Unit:


1) $ wget https://phar.phpunit.de/phpunit.phar
2) chmod +x phpunit.phar
3) sudo mv phpunit.phar /usr/local/bin/phpunit


After Install Php unit You have to update your php version

1) sudo add-apt-repository ppa:ondrej/php5-oldstable
2) sudo apt-get update
3) sudo apt-get install php5
4) sudo apt-get install python-software-properties

After this Install php PEar

		1)sudo apt-get install phppear

After this You have to install Xdebug

1) pecl install xdebug
2)udo apt-get install php5-xdebug debhelper php5-dev binutils dh-apparmor dpkg dpkg-dev file html2text man-db perl po-debconf dh-make autoconf automake libssl-dev libtool php5-common shtool ucf libc6 php5-cli


Enjoy PHP UNIT..........................
